Thank you everyone for your overwhelming support. Your love and prayers are truly helping. My wife Lauren was thankfully not with me at the time of the incident. We are together now, and working on recovering in a safe space. We are focusing on healing for everyone involved. We ask you to join us in our effort to move from confusion and shock to compassion and empathy. We understand this act of violence can be triggering for so many people. To all of the fans, veterans, and first responders in our global community we are thinking of you all. Together with love, we can all get through these difficult times.

Rick Allen & Lauren Monroe

Thank you all so very much for all of your love and support over the last month.  I am still recovering and getting my mind and body ready for the upcoming Def Leppard tour. Just wanted to say hi and let you know, There Will Be Rock! #rickallen

Not busy on September 9th/10th? Then join me in Healdsburg, CA for some fantastic charity fundraising events! Raven Drum Foundation is joining up with Chateau Diana Winery to present a special afternoon of storytelling and music.  The concert event is on the 9th where you can join us for food, drinks, a silent auction, and then a live performance featuring my wife Lauren Monroe, myself, and special guests. Those who would like to donate at the VIP level can also join us the next morning (the 10th) at 10am with a reserved seat at our Healing Drum Circle.  It will include celebrity guest drummers Alvin Taylor and Franklin Vanderbilt along with first responders, victims of the Tubbs fire, and additional special guests!  Drums will be provided as well as a Meet & Greet opportunity with Lauren & I. Plus we'll have a brunch reception after the drum circle.  Hope to see you there!  Limited tickets are available now: http://chateaudshow.givesmart.com/
#linkinbio #linktree #linktreeinbio

In support of our @ravendrumfoundation, @laurenmonroelive & I will be co-hosting a special event this September: The Mountain Rhythm Reset! Bid now through August 10th at Charity Buzz to be able to join us in beautiful Jackson Hole, Wyoming on September 21-23 as we connect with empathy, build resilience, and reimagine community with legendary drummers & musicians, inspiring military veterans, and innovative thought leaders.

Included in the event are beautiful accommodations, the great outdoors, fireside chats, one-of-a-kind drum circles, and yoga & mindfulness exercises - all on top of the transformational programming and speakers that are lined up.

Get your bid in now for a fantastic experience: https://www.charitybuzz.com/catalog_items/auction-attend-mountain-rhythm-reset-hosted-by-rock-2741400

Raven Drum serves, educates, and empowers trauma survivors and communities in crisis, with a focus on Veterans and First Responders. By integrating advocacy, storytelling, music and arts programs and events, we bring the tools and experiences of complementary and alternative medicine (CAM) to support and inspire mental health, resiliency, and unity.

!!!Ending tomorrow!!! 11/11 on Veterans Day, Raven Drum Foundation’s annual #12DrummersDrumming auction. You can join @rickallenlive , fellow musicians and drummers to support our mission and bid on some truly fantastic and unique items, including a pair of tickets to @widespreadpanichq sold out New Year’s Eve show at @thefoxtheatre with a signed show poster. This all goes towards our efforts to serve, educate and empower trauma survivors and communities in crisis, with a focus on Veterans and First Responders.

Place your bids and support the mission now at:
